            Attrition rate <button class="info-btn" data-tip="Expected % of your current team that will leave during the plan horizon. We add replacement hires to your plan automatically. Industry average for Indian tech: 18-22%. Gaming is typically higher (25-30%). Setting this makes the confidence score higher.">i</button>
